00:03:05.362 --> 00:03:10.292
Our second law is related to swans, the majestic white

00:03:10.292 --> 00:03:14.202
birds that you might see floating down a river or on a lake.

00:03:15.192 --> 00:03:18.882
There are a few strange laws relating to swans in the UK.

00:03:19.852 --> 00:03:23.902
Firstly, all swans in the UK are protected.

00:03:24.502 --> 00:03:31.882
It is illegal to kill one, and you can be given a large fine of up to £5,000 for killing a swan.

00:03:33.093 --> 00:03:37.963
Fair enough, you might think - swans seem pretty nice, who would want to kill one?

00:03:39.003 --> 00:03:42.673
